OL,4,CNew emergency text alerts to be
OL,5,Ctrialled
OL,6, A new emergency alert text system will
OL,7, be trialled this summer before being
OL,8, rolled out across the UK.
OL,10,FWarnings will be sent directly to
OL,11,Fpeople's phones in the event a risk to
OL,12,Flife, such as flooding or fire.
OL,14,FSimilar systems exist in other
OL,15,Fcountries, including New Zealand,
OL,16,F"where it has been widely credited with
OL,17,Fsaving lives," the government said.
OL,19,FThe first trial will be in East Suffolk
OL,20,Fon 25 May, when residents will receive
OL,21,Fa test alert.
